
Install MSYS2

Start an MSYS2 shell and install the ucrt compiler, plus make

    pacman -S mingw-w64-ucrt-x86_64-gcc
    pacman -S make

Use the MSYS2 UCRT64 shell, or if using another terminal, add these 2
directories to your PATH

    set PATH=c:\msys64\ucrt64\bin;c:\msys64\usr\bin;%PATH%

Build the program using make

    make

The application creates a tray icon, but has no other user interface.
Double-click on the tray icon to close the app.

Edit default_volume.ini to change the default percentage from 40.
